{"tid":2374694,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉：下載「安心出行」都忘記使用","createTime":"2021-01-21T12:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T12:11:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9a3235c472a3c2a41f3a8f383df1666498de7c5b","tid":2374694,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pDBtJWluIwOv1det_FlbiA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/8.GRiK9W6m_v04zLIpCuBQ--~B/aD03NTA7dz0xMDAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/singtao.com.hk/b5ecd4226076d1c948dc920e9d1df0db\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpDBtJWluIwOv1det_FlbiA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F8.GRiK9W6m_v04zLIpCuBQ--~B%2FaD03NTA7dz0xMDAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fsingtao.com.hk%2Fb5ecd4226076d1c948dc920e9d1df0db&h=8a88493c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】立法會今日第二日辯論施政報告致謝議案，預計明日表決，會上有議員批評政府抗疫不力。<br />\n<br />\n新民黨主席葉劉淑儀指本港新冠肺炎疫情清零無期，批評政府的檢測政策落後形勢，一直追落後，直接令到恢復經濟無期。她認為政府應採取徹底方案抗疫，如在整個區域進行檢測等。她並指，當局推出的手機應用程式「安心出行」下載量低，還坦言她即使已下載但都忘記使用。<br />\n<br />\n批發及零售界議員邵家輝指，受疫情影響，商界已五勞七傷，部分低確診甚至零確診的行業，例如美容業卻不能營業，促請政府應容許這些行業盡快局部復業。"},{"pid":"48a7ea6314023e1d4b76189c87365ec74f803429","tid":2374694,"uid":35514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:11:15.000Z","msg":"行會成員帶頭忘記使用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}